Is the golden castor sugar quantity correct at 750g this seems a very large amount?</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div></div></div></div><div id="fragment-tip" class="section-comments__single-tab-content"><div class="comment__no-comments-wrapper"><span class="comment__no-comments-title">Be the first to suggest a tip for this recipe...</span>Got your own twist on this recipe? Or do you have suggestions for possible swaps and additions? We’d love to hear your ideas.<div class="comment__no-comments-sign-in"><a href="/user/login?destination=recipes/4680/spiced-poached-pears-in-chocolate-sauce">Sign in</a> or <a href="/user/register?destination=recipes/4680/spiced-poached-pears-in-chocolate-sauce">create your My Good Food account</a> to join the discussion.</div></div></div></div> </section></div></div> <aside class="col span4"><div id="ad-mpu-premium-1-wide" class="ad-mpu-premium-1-wide"><div class="ad ad--mpu-premium-1-wide" id="ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_1_wide-ca4a274b6b"><script type="text/javascript">Drupal.GPT.createSlot("ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_1_wide-ca4a274b6b", function () {var m = Drupal.GPT.buildSizeMapping([[[0,0],[]],[[770,0],[[300,250],[300,600]]]]);var s = googletag.defineSlot(Drupal.GPT.unitPath(), m.define, "ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_1_wide-ca4a274b6b").defineSizeMapping(m.mapping.build()).setTargeting("pos", ["mpu_premium_1"]).addService(googletag.pubads());});</script></div></div><div id="ad-mpu-premium-2"><div class="ad ad--mpu-premium-2-wide" id="ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_2_wide-c41c6a458c"><script type="text/javascript">Drupal.GPT.createSlot("ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_2_wide-c41c6a458c", function () {var m = Drupal.GPT.buildSizeMapping([[[0,0],[]],[[770,0],[[300,250],[300,251]]]]);var s = googletag.defineSlot(Drupal.GPT.unitPath(), m.define, "ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_2_wide-c41c6a458c").defineSizeMapping(m.mapping.build()).setTargeting("pos", ["mpu_premium_2"]).addService(googletag.pubads());});</script></div></div><div id="block-bbcg